{"title":"没有时间的人","authors":["路工"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有时间的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早起到黑夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙得满头大汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处理了什么原则问题？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你没有想到这点……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正忙、忙、忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比蚂蚁还勤俭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问明天干什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说“到明天再看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一件事办一件！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了明天你又忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙得忘了啥时间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有两件事都要你去干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不能分身去两边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能跑东又跑西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条腿酸痛打战战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛眯眯想瞌睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办不完再等明天……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天、明天、又明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天老是没时间……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，天又半夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你没睡前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考虑下：过有计划的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载自人民铁道）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}